title: The RAGE Collection!
description:
A collection of the most blood-boiling, gear-grinding, ball-bursting rage ever seen on the internet. Includes: furries thinking they're people, general retardation, technological illiteracy, the very existence of bronies, and much, much more! Also includes some anti-rage, to calm you down when you feel like taking a gun to a local school. 
(DISCLAIMER: HEH GUY is not responsible for any heart attacks caused by the viewing of these images.)
